      "audioDurationSec": 8.515918,
      "textHash": "a21498fe88baf469e5e87a5fdacc5421eca968119651732c7f497b3afbfeabd9",
      "narrationText": "Loetleme masina repositooriumid, et kinnitada uue registreerimist. Edaspidi saab repositooriumi avada VS Code'is, juurutada, teha sellest forki või varundada -- kõik sülearvutist.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-create-repo/tutorial-create-repo-02-after.c9114639.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 2.586122,
      "afterTextHash": "c91146398b47482722e6685a418d948d2e70bbdca5fc85df81f34760fa7aa30b"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-create-repo-03",
      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 17.238181,
      "replayEndSec": 21.33289,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-create-repo/tutorial-create-repo-03.3cd1fc9a.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 12.355918,
      "textHash": "3cd1fc9aa3cf2e6cb372327b5c4eaec86b990e38b349dca1b70aea04e2410f22",
      "narrationText": "Üks kasulik võimalus: avada repo otse VS Code'is selle käsuga. Me ei käivita siin redaktorit, kuid see alustab SSH kaudu repo'sse kaugseanssi, et saaksite selle faile muuta.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-create-repo/tutorial-create-repo-03-after.fe26f5cd.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.866122,
      "afterTextHash": "fe26f5cdfb45cb2f35cdd216b0dcdbe0ed7b157299333ea00b48079d58afa5f0"
    }
  ],
  "narrationAudio": [
    {
      "id": "intro",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-create-repo/intro.d4921d84.mp3",
      "textHash": "d4921d84022408545d2681c718d8d84a3c77dae8d3adc9c769419d656ab070a9",
      "audioDurationSec": 8.907755,
      "narrationText": "Loome su esimese repositooriumi! See on puhkeolekus krüpteeritud fail, mis ühendamisel muutub täielikult isoleeritud keskkonnaks."
    },
    {
      "id": "file-on-disk",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-create-repo/file-on-disk.5083fa24.mp3",
      "textHash": "5083fa2473639e24068e94fe8890f45aafd8cde7de1b11ded47ff40b012a8c43",
      "audioDurationSec": 13.714286,
      "narrationText": "Kettal on see üksik krüpteeritud kujutis. Ühendamisel saad pühendatud Dockeri deemoni, rakenduse andmed krüpteeritud mahu sees ja loopback IP-d, mis ei kattu millegi muuga serveris."
    },
    {
